    <p>Two of the girls had <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="been on the point of marriage"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(差点就结婚了)</code></b>, and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="after all there was nothing in it"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(最后一场空)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Mrs. Bennet still continued to wonder and repine at his returning no more, and though a day seldom passed in which Elizabeth did not <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="account for it"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(解释它)</code></b> clearly, there seemed little chance of her ever considering it with less perplexity.</p>
  </li>
