    <p>Your sister is <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="crossed in love | cross - 惹...生气"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(失恋了)</code></b>, I find. I congratulate her. <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Next to"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(仅次于/意译为和...相比)</code></b> being married, a girl lilkes to be crossed in love a little now and then.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Mr. Wickham’s society was <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="of material service"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(帮助良多)</code></b> in dispelling gloom, which the late perverse occurrances had <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="thrown on"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(被...陷入某种状况)</code></b> many of the Longbourn family. They saw him often, and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="to his other recommendations was now added that of general unreverse"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(他还多了一个可贵之处，即对大家坦率)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>The Lucases are very artful people indeed, sister. <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="They are all for what they can get"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(他们为达目的不择手段)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
